{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Be the last line of defense for an entire species</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed with nanomachines, the last defender of humanity can be <strong>upgraded</strong> to shape it into <strong>powerful weapons and tools</strong>. It\u2019s up to you to choose which\u2014and, more importantly, when.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hold, upgrade, and hold again</strong> to ensure the survival of mankind\u2014all set against the backdrop of fast-paced soundtracks and nerve-wracking gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478760/extras/HFH_GIF_FIGHT.gif?t=1740586933\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Rhythmic Arms Race</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you evolve, so too does the enemy, creating increasingly complex bots to breach your defenses. <strong>Learn their patterns and master the beat to prevail</strong>, no matter how many attempts it takes, humanity's survival is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478760/extras/HFH_GIF_UPGRADE.gif?t=1740586933\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight in a arcade atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the pixel art to the animations and the sound design HOLD FOR HUMANS is soaked in the 8 bit realm to deliver you the arcade experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3478760?t=1740586933","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478760/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740586933","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478760/a2e1ebd